ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectQuebec Domestic Help Charities Remission Order
PrecisQUEBEC DOMESTIC HELP CHARITIES REMISSION ORDER, to remit the revocation tax paid or payable to certain charities that were, in addition to being a registered charity, concurrently participating in a program that provides subsidized domestic help services to residents of Quebec.
